lyrics:
bananas

[verse]
In the jungle, where the trees sway tall
Friends gather 'neath the sunlight's gall
Eating bananas, a joyous call
Voices harmonize, together we enthrall

[chorus]
Oh, we dance and sing in the wild
Beneath the stars in the nighttime mild
Together we feast, forever beguiled
Eating bananas with friends, our ecstasy compiled
